   Vnto
   Unto
the author of their balefull bane;

   Vnto
   Unto
their mind, voide of all blemishment;

   Euen
   Even
for his sake, and for his sacred word,

   Vnmindfull
   Unmindfull
of that dearest Lord of thyne;

   Neuer
   Never
consum’d nor quencht with mortall hands;

   Haue
   Have
purtrayd this, for all his maistring skill;
